        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5 CFD hemolysis solver",
        "description": "Solver must be under formal version control with traceable release history, all governing equations unit-tested, regression test suite passing at >95% coverage, and a documented configuration management plan on file with the regulatory submission."
      },
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is managed under git version control with tagged releases; regression suite achieves 96% line coverage across hemolysis-relevant modules. A configuration management plan was prepared and reviewed by the quality team. Achieved level 4 equals the required level 4 at MRL 5 for this factor; no gap exists."
    },
    {
